directions: From the entrance it’s to the left and straight into the back. Hard to miss.

Haven’t used it since my transition progress, but the bathrooms are very out there. You will be seen going in and the way to the bathroom, from my memory is kinda narrow do to the tables. 
The staff seems friendly though.

*I believe you have to be a paying customer 
*There is no other way to get up besides the stairs but the restroom is big and easily accessible

name: Hotel On North
